  "detailed_description": "<h1>Dininho Adventures</h1><p></p><br><h1>Jujubos</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1616870/extras/36d0bc2002c6028f8a379e194788223e.poster.avif?t=1631131655\" width=626 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1616870/extras/36d0bc2002c6028f8a379e194788223e.webm?t=1631131655\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1616870/extras/36d0bc2002c6028f8a379e194788223e.mp4?t=1631131655\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>In one of his daily observations, Dininho sees an imminent threat on a planet within his system.<br>Taken by a mixture of euphoria and concern, Dininho jumps into his ship and without thinking twice,<br>takes off towards what may be the most dangerous and heroic adventure of your life.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Challenging adventure full of shots and obstacles.<br></li><li> Collect coins and upgrade your ship.<br></li><li> Play the way you want (mouse, keyboard and Joypad).<br></li><li> 3 different worlds with 1 Boss each.<br></li><li> +40 different enemies and obstacles!</li></ul>",
